block content
    .hero-section
        h1 About Rocks!
        p Your premier destination for high-quality, rare, and beautiful rock specimens
    .aboutContainer
        .about
            h2.heading Our Story
            .content
                p Rocks! was founded in 2025 by geology enthusiasts fascinated by the beauty and diversity of the earth beneath our feet. From polished gemstones to rugged minerals, we’ve always believed that every rock tells a story millions of years in the making. 
                p What started as a personal collection has grown into a passion for sharing these natural treasures with fellow enthusiasts, collectors, and curious minds. Today, we source high-quality rocks and minerals from around the world to bring a little piece of Earth’s wonder into your home.
        .about
            h2.heading Our Mission
            .content
                p We’re on a mission to make rocks, minerals, and crystals accessible and meaningful for everyone. Whether you’re a collector, a hobbyist, an educator, or simply someone who loves the natural world, we aim to provide an inspiring, educational, and reliable place to discover the beauty of geology. Every piece we sell is thoughtfully selected for its uniqueness, quality, and ability to spark curiosity and joy.
        .about
            h2.heading Our Values
            .content
                span.aboutSection 🌱 Sustainability
                p.aboutBlurb We partner with suppliers who respect the environment and support responsible mining practices.
                span.aboutSection 🔍 Authenticity
                p.aboutBlurb  We guarantee that every rock, mineral, and crystal is genuine, ethically sourced, and carefully curated.
                span.aboutSection 📚 Education
                p.aboutBlurb We’re passionate about promoting geological knowledge and making learning about rocks, minerals, and earth science fun, accessible, and engaging for all ages.
                span.aboutSection 🤝 Community
                p.aboutBlurb We believe in sharing knowledge and building a community of rock lovers, young and old, around the world.
